name: 娜塔莉·D·伍达德
name_full: 娜塔莉·D·伍达德 Natalie Denise Woodard
introduction: Is an American actress known for an Intelligent and Confident on-screen presence. Earlier projects include work on a Pilot, for ABC, called "Selfie," under the direction of Julie Anne Robinson, for Piece of Pie Productions. She also had a small role, for Lifetime, on the Whitney Houston biopic, called "Whitney," directed by Angela Bassett and played on the CW sitcom "The First Family," produced by Byron Allen and Entertainment Studios. She has also worked with Kristen Bell and Nia Long on an Internet New Media Project called "Falling For You." And, in addition, to her acting talents, Natalie is also a very skilled writer having written and starred in three Shorts called "Close Encounters," "Not Always Guilty," and "The Waitress."
